6
00:00:13.847 --> 00:00:16.176
NOVA:  Prepare for the worst, you mean.

7
00:00:16.476 --> 00:00:18.273
VEGA:  Always.

8
00:00:19.323 --> 00:00:22.045
NULL:  If I can't break the walls, I'll snatch

9
00:00:22.045 --> 00:00:24.837
your secrets in transit, or wait for the

10
00:00:24.837 --> 00:00:26.023
