00:00:26.323 --> 00:00:29.334
VEGA:  Then we seal the roads, guard the vaults,

12
00:00:29.334 --> 00:00:31.170
and prepare for the dark.

13
00:00:32.220 --> 00:00:35.798
VEGA:  Layer six protects the data itself, and keeps

14
00:00:35.798 --> 00:00:38.342
