15
00:00:38.642 --> 00:00:42.982
Three families hold the line: System & Communications

16
00:00:42.982 --> 00:00:47.485
Protection, Media Protection, and Contingency Planning.

17
00:00:48.535 --> 00:00:51.021
NOVA:  SC, MP, and CP. The warden of the

18
00:00:51.021 --> 00:00:54.410
roads, the steward of scrolls, and the keeper

19
00:00:54.410 --> 00:00:55.389
of lifelines.

20
00:00:56.439 --> 00:00:59.895
VEGA:  The Warden of Walls and Roads, System and

21
00:00:59.895 --> 00:01:02.086
Communications Protection.

22
00:01:02.386 --> 00:01:06.134
VEGA:  It fortifies the ramparts and seals the roads

23
00:01:06.134 --> 00:01:07.633
