27
00:01:16.680 --> 00:01:19.109
NOVA:  What is 'the edge of the system'?

28
00:01:19.409 --> 00:01:22.959
VEGA:  Draw a line around your computers, data, and

29
00:01:22.959 --> 00:01:26.105
the people who run them. Inside is your

30
00:01:26.105 --> 00:01:28.606
system. SC-7 watches that line.

31
00:01:29.656 --> 00:01:34.138
VEGA:  SC-7, boundary protection, guards the edge of the

32
00:01:34.138 --> 00:01:34.778
system.

33
00:01:36.156 --> 00:01:39.071
NOVA:  You keep saying cryptography - what does it

34
00:01:39.071 --> 00:01:39.885
