78
00:04:16.816 --> 00:04:21.013
VEGA:  The Keeper of Lifelines, Contingency Planning.

79
00:04:21.313 --> 00:04:24.334
VEGA:  It plans for the day the towers fall,

80
00:04:24.334 --> 00:04:25.885
